date-released: 2026-03-12
version: "1.0"
abstract: >
  A framework deriving reality from a single primitive:
  distinction (delta). From delta emerge time, constraint,
  mind, suffering, and physical predictions including
  no-singularity black holes and a testable quantum
  measurement prediction.
